rying zero\nelectric charge but unit magnetic charge) and elementary dyon (carrying both\nunit electric charge and unit magnetic charge) are fermionic and bosonic,\nrespectively. In SET states, intrinsic excitations may carry fractional charge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2013 19:47:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Mar 2013 16:31:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2013 15:04:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-28"}
