 fraction ($\\sim 60%$) of the\nevents remains hidden in the unaccessible, high density nuclear regions because\nof a combination of reduced search efficiency and high extinction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2013 15:13:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
